00:10:41.340 --> 00:10:42.380
How could he do such a thing?

00:10:42.700 --> 00:10:43.380
How could he engage in such activities?

00:10:43.380 --> 00:10:44.180
We have the ledger as proof.

00:10:44.180 --> 00:10:44.820
My gosh!

00:10:46.540 --> 00:10:47.180
Quick, get a picture! Get a picture!

00:10:49.460 --> 00:10:50.780
That ledger...

00:10:50.780 --> 00:10:52.620
It's impossible for an outsider
to know about it.

00:10:55.100 --> 00:10:57.700
Has anyone been in the study
or the secret room?

00:10:59.580 --> 00:11:00.660
The patrols said only Miss Wang was seen

00:11:00.780 --> 00:11:02.860
near the study last night,

00:11:03.140 --> 00:11:04.140
